}
ğŸ‘‰ Explanation:

region â†’ AWS region where to deploy.

instance_type â†’ EC2 instance size.

ami_id â†’ AMI ID.

env â†’ environment (dev/qa/prod).

tags â†’ map variable for tagging resources.

ğŸ”¹ Step 2: Use Variables in main.tf
# main.tf

