  ami           = var.ami_id
  instance_type = var.instance_type

  tags = merge(
    var.tags,
    {
      Name = "ec2-${var.env}"
    }
  )
}
ğŸ‘‰ merge(var.tags, {...}) combines default tags with environment-specific tags.

ğŸ”¹ Step 3: Create terraform.tfvars
This file contains actual values for the variables.
You can create different .tfvars files for dev, qa, prod environments.

